title: FIAT typeface
content:
Can anyone help me identifying the typeface in the recent FIAT ads? Here is a sample:

[http://typophile.com/files/94ca5d16a4b4e29d401b8c1143ebaa2b.44077.jpeg.jpg](http://web.archive.org/web/20120119050015/http:/typophile.com/files/94ca5d16a4b4e29d401b8c1143ebaa2b.44077.jpeg.jpg)

It looks similar to a free font called Market Deco:

[http://typophile.com/files/Picture2\_0.png](http://web.archive.org/web/20120119050015/http:/typophile.com/files/Picture2_0.png)

Or a modified Neutraface:

[http://typophile.com/files/Picture3.png](http://web.archive.org/web/20120119050015/http:/typophile.com/files/Picture3.png)

Any ideas?
